{"content":"---\ntitle: \"<configSections> element for <configuration>\"\nms.date: \"05/01/2017\"\nf1_keywords: \n  - \"http://schemas.microsoft.com/.NetConfiguration/v2.0#configuration/configSections\"\nhelpviewer_keywords: \n  - \"configSections Element\"\n  - \"<configSections> Element\"\nms.assetid: 9f963c1b-dc3f-4220-a8b6-2dd7a5a8e039\nauthor: \"guardrex\"\nms.author: \"mairaw\"\n---\n\n# \\<configSections> element for \\<configuration>\n\nContains configuration section and namespace declarations.\n\n[**\\<configuration>**](~/docs/framework/configure-apps/file-schema/configuration-element.md)   \n&nbsp;&nbsp;**\\<configSections>**\n\n## Attributes\n\nNone\n\n## Parent element\n\n|     | Description |\n| --- | ----------- |\n| [**\\<configuration>**](~/docs/framework/configure-apps/file-schema/configuration-element.md) | The root element in every configuration file used by the common language runtime and .NET Framework applications. |\n\n## Child elements\n\n|     | Description |\n| --- | ----------- |\n| [**\\<section>**](~/docs/framework/configure-apps/file-schema/section-element.md) | Contains a configuration section declaration. |\n| [**\\<sectionGroup>**](~/docs/framework/configure-apps/file-schema/sectiongroup-element-for-configsections.md) | Defines a namespace for configuration sections. |\n| [**\\<remove>**](~/docs/framework/configure-apps/file-schema/remove-element-for-configsections.md) | Removes a predefined section or section group. |\n| [**\\<clear>**](~/docs/framework/configure-apps/file-schema/clear-element-for-configsections.md) | Clears all previously defined sections and section groups. |\n\n## Remarks\n\nIf this element is in a configuration file, it must be the first child element of the **\\<configuration>** element.\n\n## Example\n\nThe following example shows how to define a configuration section and define settings for that section:\n\n```xml\n<configuration>\n  <configSections>\n    <section name=\"sampleSection\"\n             type=\"System.Configuration.SingleTagSectionHandler\" />\n  </configSections>\n  <sampleSection setting1=\"Value1\" \n                 setting2=\"value two\" \n                 setting3=\"third value\" />\n</configuration>\n```\n\n## Configuration file\n\nThis element can be used in the application configuration file, machine configuration file (*Machine.config*), and *Web.config* files that are not at the application directory level.\n\n## See also\n\n- [Configuration file schema for the .NET Framework](~/docs/framework/configure-apps/file-schema/index.md)\n","nodes":[{"pos":[4,350],"embed":true,"restype":"x-metadata","content":"title: \"<configSections> element for <configuration>\"\nms.date: \"05/01/2017\"\nf1_keywords: \n  - \"http://schemas.microsoft.com/.NetConfiguration/v2.0#configuration/configSections\"\nhelpviewer_keywords: \n  - \"configSections Element\"\n  - \"<configSections> Element\"\nms.assetid: 9f963c1b-dc3f-4220-a8b6-2dd7a5a8e039\nauthor: \"guardrex\"\nms.author: \"mairaw\"","nodes":[{"content":"<configSections> element for <configuration>","nodes":[{"pos":[0,44],"content":"<ph id=\"ph1\">&lt;configSections&gt;</ph> element for <ph id=\"ph2\">&lt;configuration&gt;</ph>","source":"<configSections> element for <configuration>"}],"path":["title"],"nosxs":false}],"yml":true},{"pos":[358,404],"content":"\\<configSections> element for \\<configuration>","linkify":"\\<configSections> element for \\<configuration>","nodes":[{"content":"<ph id=\"ph1\">\\&lt;</ph>configSections&gt; element for <ph id=\"ph2\">\\&lt;</ph>configuration&gt;","pos":[0,46],"source":"\\<configSections> element for \\<configuration>"}]},{"content":"Contains configuration section and namespace declarations.","pos":[406,464]},{"content":"<bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt><bpt id=\"p2\">**</bpt><ph id=\"ph1\">\\&lt;</ph>configuration&gt;<ept id=\"p2\">**</ept><ept id=\"p1\">](~/docs/framework/configure-apps/file-schema/configuration-element.md)</ept><ph id=\"ph2\"> </ph>","pos":[466,559],"source":"[**\\<